Usage
Register: Send a POST request to http://localhost:8000/register/ with username and password.

Get JWT Token: Use the registered username and password to get JWT tokens from http://localhost:8000/api/token/.

Access Endpoints: Use the access token to authenticate and access the endpoints.

Endpoints
Register User:

POST /register/

Request: { "username": "<username>", "password": "<password>" }

Get Movies:

GET /movies/

Request Count:

GET /request-count/

Reset Request Count:

POST /request-count/reset/

Create Collection:

POST /collection/

Request: { "title": "<title>", "description": "<description>", "movies": [ ... ] }

Update Collection:

PUT /collection/<collection_uuid>/

Request: { "title": "<title>", "description": "<description>", "movies": [ ... ] }

Delete Collection:

DELETE /collection/<collection_uuid>/

